gitCommit.subject: feat(e2e): add HTML reports, artifact download, failure auto-issue
gitCommit.body:
feat(e2e): add HTML reports, artifact download, failure auto-issue

Improvements to E2E testing workflow:

1. HTML Reports in CI
   - Added HTML reporter to playwright.config.ts (CI + local)
   - Upload per-shard HTML reports as artifacts
   - Merge HTML reports in merge-reports job
   - View with: pnpm test:report

2. GitHub CLI Artifact Download Script
   - scripts/download-e2e-artifacts.ps1 using gh CLI
   - One command to download latest CI artifacts
   - Auto-extracts traces, screenshots, HTML report
   - -FailedOnly flag to get latest failure artifacts

3. Automatic Failure Issue Creation
   - .github/workflows/e2e-failure-issue.yml
   - Creates GitHub issue on E2E test failure
   - Includes debug steps and artifact links
   - Adds comment to existing issue if <24h old

4. Incremental Test Selection
   - scripts/test-affected.ps1 analyzes git diff
   - Maps changed files to relevant test patterns
   - Runs only affected tests for faster feedback
   - -DryRun flag to preview without running

New package.json scripts:
- pnpm ci:artifacts         - Download latest CI artifacts
- pnpm ci:artifacts:failed  - Download from latest failed run
- pnpm ci:show-trace        - View Playwright trace files
- pnpm test:e2e:ci-mode     - Run E2E with production build
- pnpm test:affected        - Run tests for changed files
- pnpm test:affected:dry    - Preview affected tests
